subject: Good Day,
body:
Good Day,
Sorry for intruding into your privacy!
Can we work together as partners in supplying raw materials to our company? I am an employee of a multi-national animal vaccine production company in the USA and UK working as the production manager.
This business is very profitable
Looking forward to your response.
Kindly reply to the corresponding Email;
Thanks,
Mr. Russell

subject: Re: Good Day,
body:
Hello Mr. Russell,

Good day to you too! I'm intrigued by your proposal and would love to learn more about it. Could you please provide more details about the type of raw materials your company requires? Also, could you tell me a bit more about how this partnership would work?

Looking forward to hearing from you.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Lucille
